{"tid":1257060,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱發夢買裝備嗰陣唔小心用咗信用咭","createTime":"2019-06-25T10:52:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T05:43:20.000Z","uid":5735,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9d045060eb9161e688151c2ef817a2068bef1ecb","tid":1257060,"uid":5735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T10:52:56.000Z","msg":"咁多位巴打我想問我頭先發夢買裝備嗰陣唔小心用咗信用咭買野，咁我d裝備係咪全部作廢㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇d咩方法可以解決呀？<br />\n係前線交換裝備？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f891dddad2f270ac856e318dab1af20dc937f363","tid":1257060,"uid":25431,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T10:53:36.000Z","msg":"如果以n年一遇嘅G20+政治風波<br />\n只要求撤回<br />\n我會覺得太可惜 點解我哋永遠都係比人打到埋牆角先識反擊？<br />\n點解唔好好借呢次機會 爭取我哋應得嘅<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">普選</span></span></strong><br />\n免除日後比人打埋牆角嘅機會呢？<br />\n<br />\n大家要食住個勢 提出更有利香港日後發展嘅要求<br />\n咁先叫升級㗎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家暫時民意大好 加埋後生仔做街站<br />\n其實教育大眾都唔係難事<br />\n仲有機會r埋班淺藍嘅民意<br />\n<br />\n而且以普世價值+基本法本身有承諾過普選呢件事 同國際講<br />\n可以攞到更多關注<br />\n<br />\n我唔係話我哋要放棄之前嘅四點訴求<br />\n而係開拓更重要嘅第五訴求<br />\n林奠落完台 又派返個中共党員管我哋 有撚用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望喺向G20請願同國際公開信入面 都可以加入我哋嘅第五訴求：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">普選</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b93edd354419289f8e4883a5c703188209afed16","tid":1257060,"uid":1643,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T10:54:50.000Z","msg":"你唔好出現喺現場"},{"pid":"1a694008ef5af70f156be395af9a0dad712b9f7f","tid":1257060,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T10:55:25.000Z","msg":"下世小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif